{"lang":"zh","stage":7,"title":"fuller sentences","sentences":[{"t":"他从三月就开始找工作了。","en":"He's been looking for a job since March.","r":"Tā cóng sānyuè jiù kāishǐ zhǎo gōngzuò le.","a":"n_4e9ca8a36b11.mp3"},{"t":"一共三十欧元。","en":"It all comes to thirty euros.","r":"Yígòng sānshí ōuyuán.","a":"n_2d8c3d65b0c0.mp3"},{"t":"我们一点吃饭。","en":"We eat at one.","r":"Wǒmen yì diǎn chīfàn.","a":"n_871e408bc229.mp3"},{"t":"我五点下班。","en":"I finish at five.","r":"Wǒ wǔ diǎn xiàbān.","a":"n_81ef9101ef8b.mp3"},{"t":"周日我睡得很多。","en":"On Sundays I sleep a lot.","r":"Zhōurì wǒ shuì de hěn duō.","a":"n_2e48af9a0c2d.mp3"},{"t":"我周六不上班。","en":"I don't work on Saturday.","r":"Wǒ zhōuliù bú shàngbān.","a":"n_be20434e5acc.mp3"},{"t":"周四见。","en":"See you on Thursday.","r":"Zhōusì jiàn.","a":"n_247094f3c175.mp3"},{"t":"我们几点开始？","en":"What time do we start?","r":"Wǒmen jǐ diǎn kāishǐ?","a":"n_71bc3c0e65f6.mp3"},{"t":"今天是我生日。","en":"Today is my birthday.","r":"Jīntiān shì wǒ shēngrì.","a":"n_4fadd8cc996b.mp3"},{"t":"你又迟到了。","en":"You're late again.","r":"Nǐ yòu chídào le.","a":"n_3f5e7ca0eccc.mp3"},{"t":"这两个一共多少钱？","en":"How much are the two of them?","r":"Zhè liǎng ge yígòng duōshao qián?","a":"n_581e662d9894.mp3"},{"t":"你卖多少钱？","en":"How much are you selling it for?","r":"Nǐ mài duōshao qián?","a":"n_95a04841168a.mp3"},{"t":"今天进场免费。","en":"Getting in is free today.","r":"Jīntiān jìnchǎng miǎnfèi.","a":"n_8ce85ea1ad53.mp3"},{"t":"我肚子疼。","en":"My stomach hurts.","r":"Wǒ dùzi téng.","a":"n_d0bc6a08b7c2.mp3"},{"t":"我背疼。","en":"My back hurts.","r":"Wǒ bèi téng.","a":"n_9bc910ff7aaa.mp3"},{"t":"我眼睛疼。","en":"My eyes hurt.","r":"Wǒ yǎnjing téng.","a":"n_f82ec5ac6ed3.mp3"},{"t":"我给你介绍一下安娜。","en":"Let me introduce you to Ana.","r":"Wǒ gěi nǐ jièshào yíxià Ānnà.","a":"n_7996f9c6c8e6.mp3"},{"t":"我在家无聊死了。","en":"I'm bored at home.","r":"Wǒ zài jiā wúliáo sǐ le.","a":"n_bb7072d08962.mp3"},{"t":"她需要更多钱。","en":"She needs more money.","r":"Tā xūyào gèng duō qián.","a":"n_7a18aa97a5c2.mp3"},{"t":"我待会儿可以看。","en":"I can see it later.","r":"Wǒ dāihuìr kěyǐ kàn.","a":"n_1c9848a1c73c.mp3"},{"t":"你是来还是留下？","en":"Are you coming or staying?","r":"Nǐ shì lái háishi liúxià?","a":"n_b74652ff6df9.mp3"},{"t":"她在做晚饭。","en":"She's making dinner.","r":"Tā zài zuò wǎnfàn.","a":"n_e7a34d551d1e.mp3"},{"t":"我问个小问题。","en":"I'll ask a quick question.","r":"Wǒ wèn ge xiǎo wèntí.","a":"n_5a85618ce852.mp3"},{"t":"我昨晚收拾好了包。","en":"I packed my bag last night.","r":"Wǒ zuówǎn shōushi hǎo le bāo.","a":"n_d643e36eb83f.mp3"},{"t":"别逗我笑。","en":"Don't make me laugh.","r":"Bié dòu wǒ xiào.","a":"n_785104c1cee6.mp3"},{"t":"我待会儿跟你说。","en":"I'll tell you about it later.","r":"Wǒ dāihuìr gēn nǐ shuō.","a":"n_227e88a4ab20.mp3"},{"t":"谁告诉你的？","en":"Who told you?","r":"Shéi gàosu nǐ de?","a":"n_783f4c6e8fdf.mp3"},{"t":"你从不跟我说什么。","en":"You never tell me anything.","r":"Nǐ cóng bù gēn wǒ shuō shénme.","a":"n_bb4beb6f4267.mp3"},{"t":"我不知道那家餐厅。","en":"I don't know that restaurant.","r":"Wǒ bù zhīdào nà jiā cāntīng.","a":"n_bc347b704dde.mp3"},{"t":"我看不出区别。","en":"I don't see the difference.","r":"Wǒ kàn bu chū qūbié.","a":"n_4071f8f46c96.mp3"},{"t":"我想给你看个东西。","en":"I want to show you something.","r":"Wǒ xiǎng gěi nǐ kàn ge dōngxi.","a":"n_1f4e9a4dcd8d.mp3"},{"t":"别那样看我。","en":"Don't look at me like that.","r":"Bié nàyàng kàn wǒ.","a":"n_0544b8d678a8.mp3"},{"t":"我们这周工作好多。","en":"We're working a lot this week.","r":"Wǒmen zhè zhōu gōngzuò hǎoduō.","a":"n_194efb19c562.mp3"},{"t":"能把面包递给我吗？","en":"Can you pass me the bread?","r":"Néng bǎ miànbāo dì gěi wǒ ma?","a":"n_86adf23696e5.mp3"},{"t":"我朋友们住在附近。","en":"My friends live nearby.","r":"Wǒ péngyoumen zhù zài fùjìn.","a":"n_d1a89eb46896.mp3"},{"t":"我们四点开始。","en":"We start at four.","r":"Wǒmen sì diǎn kāishǐ.","a":"n_2b834ede7bed.mp3"},{"t":"十二月很冷。","en":"It's cold in December.","r":"Shí'èryuè hěn lěng.","a":"n_9f1b2660d649.mp3"},{"t":"我的表不准。","en":"My watch is wrong.","r":"Wǒ de biǎo bù zhǔn.","a":"n_a144a263cd9c.mp3"},{"t":"我待会儿解释。","en":"I'll explain later.","r":"Wǒ dāihuìr jiěshì.","a":"n_47b9572fe8db.mp3"},{"t":"我今天起晚了。","en":"I got up late today.","r":"Wǒ jīntiān qǐ wǎn le.","a":"n_4a2357b9ba69.mp3"},{"t":"你来得正好。","en":"You're right on time.","r":"Nǐ lái de zhèng hǎo.","a":"n_9358e77bc0ee.mp3"},{"t":"我能刷卡吗？","en":"Can I pay by card?","r":"Wǒ néng shuākǎ ma?","a":"n_c06c484616e7.mp3"},{"t":"我在哪儿叫停出租车？","en":"Where do I stop the taxi?","r":"Wǒ zài nǎr jiào tíng chūzūchē?","a":"n_f2ee2f718dc1.mp3"},{"t":"我老是错过火车。","en":"I always miss the train.","r":"Wǒ lǎoshi cuòguò huǒchē.","a":"n_d31dc5506456.mp3"},{"t":"我一颗牙疼。","en":"One of my teeth hurts.","r":"Wǒ yì kē yá téng.","a":"n_13da4ad86588.mp3"},{"t":"昨天我去看电影了。","en":"Yesterday I went to the movies.","r":"Zuótiān wǒ qù kàn diànyǐng le.","a":"n_1df36b210017.mp3"},{"t":"我脚疼。","en":"My feet hurt.","r":"Wǒ jiǎo téng.","a":"n_371ba8ce2201.mp3"},{"t":"照照镜子看看自己。","en":"Look at yourself in the mirror.","r":"Zhàozhao jìngzi kànkan zìjǐ.","a":"n_b1fa08763a74.mp3"},{"t":"我从来没试过。","en":"I've never tried it.","r":"Wǒ cónglái méi shì guò.","a":"n_2ac0cc6a1ef0.mp3"},{"t":"你周六去哪儿了？","en":"Where did you go on Saturday?","r":"Nǐ zhōuliù qù nǎr le?","a":"n_c0636945ad3c.mp3"},{"t":"你得吃点东西。","en":"You have to eat something.","r":"Nǐ děi chī diǎn dōngxi.","a":"n_cba509320532.mp3"},{"t":"不，那不是我。","en":"No, that's not me.","r":"Bù, nà bú shì wǒ.","a":"n_870241d3111d.mp3"},{"t":"我挺好的，你呢？","en":"I'm good, and you?","r":"Wǒ tǐng hǎo de, nǐ ne?","a":"n_965e0ec864ba.mp3"},{"t":"我想做什么就做什么。","en":"I do what I want.","r":"Wǒ xiǎng zuò shénme jiù zuò shénme.","a":"n_b5114a1314b3.mp3"},{"t":"我能做的我都做。","en":"I do what I can.","r":"Wǒ néng zuò de wǒ dōu zuò.","a":"n_33610689e3bc.mp3"},{"t":"你得多睡点。","en":"You have to sleep more.","r":"Nǐ děi duō shuì diǎn.","a":"n_9574f2650cd0.mp3"},{"t":"你明天得上班吗？","en":"Do you have to work tomorrow?","r":"Nǐ míngtiān děi shàngbān ma?","a":"n_0c225a3d9d3f.mp3"},{"t":"看看我有什么。","en":"Look what I've got.","r":"Kànkan wǒ yǒu shénme.","a":"n_acf11706c116.mp3"},{"t":"对，这儿疼。","en":"Yes, it hurts here.","r":"Duì, zhèr téng.","a":"n_f3ae29abd62b.mp3"},{"t":"我累但很开心。","en":"I'm tired but happy.","r":"Wǒ lèi dàn hěn kāixīn.","a":"n_354d1c65e916.mp3"},{"t":"我饿了，得吃点东西。","en":"I'm hungry, I need to eat.","r":"Wǒ è le, děi chī diǎn dōngxi.","a":"n_5ad6b37092f1.mp3"},{"t":"我起床然后吃饭。","en":"I get up and eat.","r":"Wǒ qǐchuáng ránhòu chīfàn.","a":"n_ac959e3915f3.mp3"},{"t":"我想点餐，麻烦了。","en":"I'd like to order, please.","r":"Wǒ xiǎng diǎncān, máfan le.","a":"n_10389bd14f58.mp3"},{"t":"我知道你是对的。","en":"I know you're right.","r":"Wǒ zhīdào nǐ shì duì de.","a":"n_1633d6ab3d84.mp3"},{"t":"我觉得你说得对。","en":"I think you're right.","r":"Wǒ juéde nǐ shuō de duì.","a":"n_76e15d12f1ee.mp3"},{"t":"你看，这是卡洛斯。","en":"Look, this is Carlos.","r":"Nǐ kàn, zhè shì Kǎluòsī.","a":"n_a5a33249c894.mp3"},{"t":"我今天得学习。","en":"I have to study today.","r":"Wǒ jīntiān děi xuéxí.","a":"n_d09bead41948.mp3"},{"t":"不用，这样就行。","en":"No, that's fine.","r":"Bú yòng, zhèyàng jiù xíng.","a":"n_dd94f1c29bb1.mp3"},{"t":"我什么都不需要，谢谢。","en":"I don't need anything, thanks.","r":"Wǒ shénme dōu bù xūyào, xièxie.","a":"n_b8f926afcc42.mp3"},{"t":"谢谢，很远吗？","en":"Thanks, is it very far?","r":"Xièxie, hěn yuǎn ma?","a":"n_fc2ceb7e48ef.mp3"},{"t":"我知道我能做到。","en":"I know I can do it.","r":"Wǒ zhīdào wǒ néng zuòdào.","a":"n_a3d6982bf6b2.mp3"},{"t":"你能做到的，我知道。","en":"You can do it, I know it.","r":"Nǐ néng zuòdào de, wǒ zhīdào.","a":"n_8300d8e5fde5.mp3"},{"t":"我宁愿自己来，谢谢。","en":"I'd rather do it alone, thanks.","r":"Wǒ nìngyuàn zìjǐ lái, xièxie.","a":"n_81dff4d3c2b7.mp3"},{"t":"我先工作再吃饭。","en":"I work and then eat.","r":"Wǒ xiān gōngzuò zài chīfàn.","a":"n_86e7e77bd62a.mp3"},{"t":"对，她叫安娜。","en":"Yes, her name is Ana.","r":"Duì, tā jiào Ānnà.","a":"n_37bf2ad71f1b.mp3"},{"t":"我们现在得走了。","en":"We have to leave now.","r":"Wǒmen xiànzài děi zǒu le.","a":"n_ca6d87d5022e.mp3"},{"t":"我们都得去吗？","en":"Do we all have to go?","r":"Wǒmen dōu děi qù ma?","a":"n_2793396f9bc3.mp3"},{"t":"你说得对，我得休息。","en":"You're right, I need to rest.","r":"Nǐ shuō de duì, wǒ děi xiūxi.","a":"n_7cb7e00bafc9.mp3"},{"t":"你得看看这个。","en":"You have to see this.","r":"Nǐ děi kànkan zhège.","a":"n_d42b9b150055.mp3"},{"t":"买单，麻烦了。","en":"The check, please.","r":"Mǎidān, máfan le.","a":"n_2f70c667c44a.mp3"},{"t":"不，我是墨西哥人。","en":"No, I'm from Mexico.","r":"Bù, wǒ shì Mòxīgē rén.","a":"n_b4aebfb4250a.mp3"},{"t":"对，她是我朋友。","en":"Yes, she's my friend.","r":"Duì, tā shì wǒ péngyou.","a":"n_2b1ddfa89a37.mp3"},{"t":"嗯，我真的好饿。","en":"Yeah, I'm really hungry.","r":"Èn, wǒ zhēn de hǎo è.","a":"n_d0ebd50cbda2.mp3"},{"t":"我吃得比你多。","en":"I ate more than you.","r":"Wǒ chī de bǐ nǐ duō.","a":"n_b63590aa2214.mp3"},{"t":"嗨，我叫卡洛斯。","en":"Hi, my name is Carlos.","r":"Hāi, wǒ jiào Kǎluòsī.","a":"n_f6740540e0e6.mp3"},{"t":"你得有点耐心。","en":"You need to have patience.","r":"Nǐ děi yǒudiǎn nàixīn.","a":"n_59cd8478853d.mp3"},{"t":"告诉他我在路上了。","en":"Tell him I'm on my way.","r":"Gàosu tā wǒ zài lùshàng le.","a":"n_a0979add21cb.mp3"},{"t":"跟他说我很抱歉。","en":"Tell him I'm sorry.","r":"Gēn tā shuō wǒ hěn bàoqiàn.","a":"n_9cc994bb47b6.mp3"},{"t":"很高兴认识你，我是卡洛斯。","en":"Nice to meet you, I'm Carlos.","r":"Hěn gāoxìng rènshi nǐ, wǒ shì Kǎluòsī.","a":"n_ca82179bb61e.mp3"},{"t":"很高兴认识你，我叫安娜。","en":"Nice to meet you, my name is Ana.","r":"Hěn gāoxìng rènshi nǐ, wǒ jiào Ānnà.","a":"n_68d038c7cbb0.mp3"},{"t":"我得跟你说件事。","en":"I have to tell you something.","r":"Wǒ děi gēn nǐ shuō jiàn shì.","a":"n_33d7e2e2b1ad.mp3"},{"t":"看这儿，不是那儿。","en":"Look here, not there.","r":"Kàn zhèr, bú shì nàr.","a":"n_d6e88985c5e0.mp3"},{"t":"我付多了，我知道。","en":"I paid too much, I know.","r":"Wǒ fù duō le, wǒ zhīdào.","a":"n_4f166db8c527.mp3"},{"t":"我觉得我发烧了。","en":"I think I have a fever.","r":"Wǒ juéde wǒ fāshāo le.","a":"n_bb0ff1122910.mp3"}]}